<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>커뮤니티 - RANKING AI</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #0b0c0d; color: #fff; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; margin: 0; }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
        .header-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 15px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; background: #121314; }
        .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: #ff5722; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        
        .write-box { background: #161718; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 30px; border: 1px solid #333; }
        input[type="text"], textarea { width: 100%; background: #222; border: 1px solid #444; color: #fff; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        textarea { height: 100px; resize: vertical; }
        .btn-submit { background: #ff5722; color: #000; border: none; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; float: right; }
        
        .post-list { clear: both; padding-top: 20px; }
        .post-card { background: #161718; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #222; }
        .post-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #ff5722; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .post-author { font-size: 13px; color: #888; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .post-content { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #ddd; white-space: pre-wrap; }
        .btn-delete { background: none; border: none; color: #ff4a4a; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; float: right; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-top">
        <div class="logo">RANKING AI 커뮤니티</div>
        <a href="/" style="color:#aaa; font-weight:bold;">🏠 메인 차트로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="write-box">
            <h3 style="margin-top:0;">✏️ 자유롭게 글을 남겨보세요</h3>
            <form action="/add-post" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="글 제목을 입력하세요" required>
                <textarea name="content" placeholder="내용을 입력하세요..." required></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">게시글 등록</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="post-list">
            <% if (posts && posts.length > 0) { %>
                <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
                    <div class="post-card">
                        <div class="post-title">
                            <%= post.title %>
                            <% if (user && (user.id === post.author || user.role === 'admin')) { %>
                                <form action="/delete-post/<%= post._id %>" method="POST" style="display:inline;" onsubmit="return confirm('삭제하시겠습니까?');">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn-delete">🗑️ 삭제</button>
                                </form>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-author">작성자: <%= post.author %> | 작성일: <%= post.createdAt.toLocaleDateString() %></div>
                        <div class="post-content"><%= post.content %></div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <p style="text-align:center; color:#666; padding: 50px;">아직 작성된 글이 없습니다. 첫 번째 글을 남겨주세요!</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
